abstract: >-
  SAFE-MCP is a comprehensive security framework for documenting and
  mitigating threats in the Model Context Protocol (MCP) ecosystem.
  It provides a structured approach to identifying, categorizing, and
  defending against attacks targeting MCP implementations and
  AI-powered applications.
